title: FABO GEEK - D UP In The Trap! Wit DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller And Chico Bean ($2) | Ep. 260

description:
On this special episode, FABO from D4L breaks down how all his hit songs came to be and shares insight on the impact of Shawty Lo. And he tells us bout the first time he saw spaceships on bankhead and who Barbara is. You know Fabo had to bring the energy, bust a freestyle and he explains his defintion of what geek'd up is. Plus, DC and Fabo gives Chico a breakdown of ATLANTA zones and Karlous Miller holds it down asking all the questions the fans want to know! You gotta hear Fabo tell the story of when them young boys jumped on em.
